output.analysis:
Let's analyze this post according to our criteria:
1. CMF Number: Yes, present as "CUI MFC 11240014" - this indicates electoral material
2. Refers to candidate: Yes, directly mentions "George Simion" who is a presidential candidate
3. Addresses wide population: Yes, this is a paid advertisement on Facebook/Instagram with significant reach (9,000-9,999 impressions)
4. Electoral objective: Yes, clearly electoral: - Uses hashtag #VoteazăAUR - Explicitly asks people to "Vino la vot" - Promotes "Planul Simion" - Uses electoral campaign rhetoric
5. Journalism: No, this is clearly campaign material, not journalistic content
6. Personal opinion: No, this is an official party communication (AUR Vâlcea) with paid distribution
The post is clearly electoral propaganda as it meets all criteria under Article 36(7): - Directly refers to a candidate (George Simion) - Used during campaign period - Has clear electoral objective - Is not journalistic content

conclusion.electoral-propaganda-analysis: This is clearly electoral propaganda because: - Contains official campaign identifiers (MFC number) - Directly promotes a candidate (George Simion) - Makes explicit call to vote - Uses campaign messaging and hashtags - Is paid partisan communication
conclusion.message-for-police: Alianța pentru Unirea Românilor Vâlcea, pentru incalcarea articolului 55 t) din Legea 370/2004, prin continuarea propagandei electorale după încheierea campaniei, materializată prin postarea cu ID-ul 914482113515376 pe Facebook, care promovează direct candidatul George Simion și solicită explicit votul cetățenilor ("Vino la vot"). Postarea este plătită și distribuită activ după ora 18:00 pe 23.11.2024, conține elemente clare de propagandă electorală (CUI MFC 11240014), și vizează influențarea directă a votului pentru alegerile prezidențiale.
